{"id":"1cb555b8-84a6-4eee-aae5-fba09aa5915a","name":"Biwa Hayahide (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 47, 98);\"><strong><em>Banana Fiend<br>ハヤヒデ</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ ───🧩─── ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/MzU1XOZvultdDpk9hDxqA.webp\" style=\"width: 499px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ⋆ ─── 🧩 ─── ⋆ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A fiery intellectual. Logic is her weapon!</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A theorist through and through, she breaks down any problem systemically. Theory-driven as she is, she values practical application, so her methods never end up as just talk.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 47, 98);\"><strong><em><br>\"This is how you derive victory!\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/YOLHaNNxQ5Azhh8I32pn3.webp\" style=\"width: 538px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ⋆ ─── 🧩 ─── ⋆ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 47, 98);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 47, 98);\"><strong><br><em>1) Too close.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 47, 98);\"><strong><em>2) Midnight banana raid</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 47, 98);\"><strong><em>3) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tTS9KzD1mrq17grDq1Y0k.webp\" style=\"width: 371px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ⋆ ─── 🧩 ─── ⋆ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:<br>3 headed monster.<br><br>I don't know about you guys, but i despises bananas. I'm literally traumatized from eating them since kindergarten.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── ⋆ ─── 🧩 ─── ⋆ ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/134391427\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/OOO8_Q/status/1919668236267733054/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@OOO8_Q (Twitter)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/88532209\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/Starbind_S/status/1969763819242074192\" target=\"_blank\">@Starbind_S</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"1Lvx_8BeU78hQhJ1sVBPl.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1910,"messages":32706,"created_at":"2025-09-30T11:21:43.136887+00:00"}